{"tid":271434,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎討論下NBA 劇本","createTime":"2017-06-05T05:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T14:43:48.000Z","uid":54581,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83c4dc8583ddf656fb57231cfd46de888f400203","tid":271434,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"其實個劇本由上年開始寫起<br />\n<br />\n雷霆俾人反cup後，杜記過檔勇士<br />\n造成佢反骨，契弟既形象 ，簡稱係奸角<br />\n<br />\n去到今年，貌似有哈登，西書 kawhi彈起<br />\n<br />\n可惜全部都是配角，一一俾大奸角~勇士同正氣凜然既主角~吾皇掃低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到Final, 杜蘭特條契弟carry起成個series, 仲有3個prime all-star坐陣<br />\n<br />\n婉如一個Final 大Boss咁撚樣，打到騎士一仆一碌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後唔洗講，占士係落後3場情況下變身超撒4 ， 而成班勇士一定有傷/病/唔在狀態<br />\n<br />\n歷史性反cup 4場<br />\n<br />\n最後乜柒霸者，皇帝等都不足以形容占士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計下條數，轉播費，週邊費用，打造左一個超越MJ既吾皇帶來既話題性、廣告、相關消費， 再加埋依家買左勇士win既賭仔身家<br />\n<br />\n屌你老尾 諗下NBA同個盤都賺到嘻一聲笑出黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以識賭一定all in 騎士<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UascE6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUascE6Y.jpg&h=16dad86d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da1a875f86fb2a014175afd602a51f5efa5f04bc","tid":271434,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"話我鳩up既放長雙眼睇<br />\n<br />\n到時遂個bin你C"},{"pid":"cb192b5a079ab18bcf05162d0d6046417cd93fd5","tid":271434,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話我鳩up既放長雙眼睇<br />\n<br />\n到時遂個bin你C</blockquote><br />\nlm"},{"pid":"4a375652c16be6206956ffa3645f4022ebb1944b","tid":271434,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"淨係見到兩個prime allstar"},{"pid":"735ea8866ff65fcc4cd88db7472fe7315a829c84","tid":271434,"uid":114774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f89fff2abca3bb9709c38943a24caae96822f1a7","tid":271434,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT